{
  "stem": "15197.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the houses were full of beliefs, of hope, of belief in humanity, of justice, and this was a chain leading to active resistance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is why I cannot separate the uprising or active resistance or the partizan resistance from the resistance which took place in the quiet, so-called times in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the base, the foundation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the foundation goes even before the war, the outbreak of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was a chain of resistance in our Jewish life, which culmination was the armed resistance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It started-- my armed resistance-- I would not say armed resistance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say resistance was all the time in the ghetto, before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My involvement in preparation for the uprising started from these small, little groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this were the groups from all kind of political youth movements.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hashomer Hatzair, the Bund, the communists, the-- the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Habonim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They created later on when deportation was going on and with-- in the beginning, we didn't know that it really deportation meant death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember when some streets were blocked, blockades were set, and they started to take the Jews out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We thought at that time that the Jews in the beginning are going to other cities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just resettlement to the east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the Warsaw ghetto we saw resettlement from the west.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Jews were coming from the German part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Jews were coming from the north, and they were coming to the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we understood that now, probably, deportation will go to other cities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother was very much concerned that if she will be caught and deported she will be by herself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she broke her leg in the beginning of the war, which was constantly bothering her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the father was no more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
